<div class="title">A Strategy to Relieve the Muscle Tension</div>
<div class="substance">AMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=neutopia&Exact=1">neutopia</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; neutopia. "A Strategy to Relieve the Muscle Tension: An Experience with AMT (exp27112)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 20, 2004. erowid.org/exp/27112</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
